<p begin="24020000t" end="38920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40040000t" end="73030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74070000t" end="142100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260260000t" end="303600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304630000t" end="374260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="414740000t" end="496090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="516510000t" end="531750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532860000t" end="565510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566560000t" end="618210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619280000t" end="668880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670000000t" end="732000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="801460000t" end="830810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第18話 同伴&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1217880000t" end="1233460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;是因為這條皮帶吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1286950000t" end="1304240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;奇怪,還不行嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1327990000t" end="1355970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;只能請你習慣這裡的保全系統了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1386710000t" end="1400700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;那這樣如何?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1425420000t" end="1435310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;大家早安&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1469130000t" end="1493810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;你的額頭是怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1500490000t" end="1515730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;被發現了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1516840000t" end="1549830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;沒什麼,跟老婆吵架了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1550880000t" end="1592180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;而且我孩子還小&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我可能不能整天待在這裡了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1598260000t" end="1629200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;是啊,下班後還是回家比較好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1630290000t" end="1667950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;真可惜,這裡的房間很棒耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1669000000t" end="1693000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;乾脆全家都搬過來就好啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1694020000t" end="1732020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;不要把我跟你這種單身漢&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;相提並論&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1733060000t" end="1743640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;龍崎呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1744740000t" end="1758390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;在約會&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1759420000t" end="1787750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;在MISAMISA的房間&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還有月,3個人一起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1804800000t" end="1819130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;監視器嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1820150000t" end="1875440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;考慮到她可能和第二KIRA有關聯&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這麼做也是不得已的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1876540000t" end="1906460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;不過松田&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;別再叫她MISAMISA了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1911910000t" end="1921230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;好的…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1929920000t" end="1971900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;我說,這樣怎麼能叫約會呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1972970000t" end="1996970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;請不要在意我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1997990000t" end="2023590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;先不說這個,你不吃蛋糕嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2024680000t" end="2051300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;甜食會發胖,我要節制&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2052380000t" end="2091060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;就算吃甜食&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只要多動腦就不會變胖了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2099090000t" end="2117740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;你又取笑我了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2118780000t" end="2158710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;那蛋糕給你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;讓我和月單獨約會可以嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2159820000t" end="2210450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;就算讓你們獨處&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我也會看監視器,還不是一樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2211540000t" end="2242140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;變態&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你就不能改掉這種壞毛病嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2243240000t" end="2276570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;隨便你怎麼說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不過蛋糕我就收下了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2277600000t" end="2312180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;也行啊&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我會關燈,拉上窗簾的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2313310000t" end="2335260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;我們也有紅外線攝影機的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2346670000t" end="2359980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;別說這個了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2361020000t" end="2389000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;好不容易有了設備齊全的總部&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2390050000t" end="2417350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;可是龍崎&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你好像完全沒有幹勁了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2428090000t" end="2441740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;幹勁嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2455110000t" end="2469440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;的確沒有&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2470460000t" end="2491390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;其實我情緒很低落&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2492490000t" end="2506140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;情緒低落?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2507170000t" end="2516490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2528850000t" end="2579480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;因為我一直認為月是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2580570000t" end="2611510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;這個推理卻不成立,真是打擊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2625950000t" end="2658940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;不,我還是對你抱有懷疑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2659990000t" end="2675570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;所以才這麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2682340000t" end="2716700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;但是KIRA可以操控人的行動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2723720000t" end="2774690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;也就是說KIRA曾經操控你們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而讓我懷疑你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2784780000t" end="2820050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;你和海砂都曾經被KIRA操控過&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2821150000t" end="2859150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;這麼一想的話,就合乎邏輯了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2870530000t" end="2883840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;這麼看來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2884880000t" end="2926180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;我和海砂都曾被操控&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以曾經是KIRA嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2927250000t" end="2965250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;是的,我想不會錯的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2966290000t" end="2981530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;你們都是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3012000000t" end="3050000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;在我看來,被囚禁時的月是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3060050000t" end="3099640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;自從你被囚禁後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就沒有罪犯死亡了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3107100000t" end="3144410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;從這點推論出你是KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;非常合理&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3145470000t" end="3184490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;可是兩個星期後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;罪犯又開始死亡了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3200860000t" end="3227480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;由此又可以推斷出一件事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3237900000t" end="3263150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;KIRA的力量轉給別人了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3279600000t" end="3293930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;你的想法很有意思&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3294950000t" end="3332260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;真是如此&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;要抓住KIRA可不容易呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3333330000t" end="3358930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;是啊,所以我很煩惱&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3366020000t" end="3387970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;即使抓住了被操控的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3389050000t" end="3424320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;力量又會轉移到其他人身上&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而不留證據&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3425420000t" end="3450100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;這樣的話,不管抓多少人都沒用&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3455780000t" end="3495140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;不過還不能斷定就是這樣吧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;拿出幹勁來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3502830000t" end="3533770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;幹勁?才提不起來呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3534860000t" end="3561480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;不,還是不要太努力比較好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3572230000t" end="3617510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;就算拚命追捕&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也只會讓自己陷入危險&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3626620000t" end="3640270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;你不這麼認為嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3666660000t" end="3676330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3756750000t" end="3770060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;不要啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3837160000t" end="3855130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;很痛耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3856180000t" end="3867440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;別胡鬧了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3868530000t" end="3884800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;因為我不是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3885880000t" end="3916820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;因為自己的推理不成立&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就失去幹勁了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3932260000t" end="3960590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle87">&#x202a;可能我的說法不太好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3961620000t" end="3988580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle88">&#x202a;我是說我們可能會做白工&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還是放棄比較好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3989650000t" end="4024570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle89">&#x202a;要是不繼續追捕&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;怎麼可能抓得住他呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4025680000t" end="4056960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle90">&#x202a;對於那些受連累無辜的被害人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你又作何感想?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4064390000t" end="4092370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle91">&#x202a;而且是你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;把我和海砂囚禁起來的吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4101760000t" end="4115750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle92">&#x202a;我也知道&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4124450000t" end="4157780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle93">&#x202a;不過,不管有什麼理由…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4192180000t" end="4211180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle94">&#x202a;我是不願意吃虧的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4359680000t" end="4379930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle95">&#x202a;比起推理不成立&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4381040000t" end="4398670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle96">&#x202a;夜神月等於KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4399720000t" end="4438740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle97">&#x202a;彌海砂等於第二KIRA的結論&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但卻沒能解決案件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4445440000t" end="4468080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle98">&#x202a;所以讓我有點沮喪&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4469130000t" end="4492790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle99">&#x202a;身為人,就不能有點情緒嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4493820000t" end="4508490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle100">&#x202a;這樣可不行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4509500000t" end="4529180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle101">&#x202a;而且你這種說法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4530190000t" end="4559880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle102">&#x202a;好像我不是KIRA你就不滿意似的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4568890000t" end="4602220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle103">&#x202a;月不是KIRA我就不滿意&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4603260000t" end="4622940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle104">&#x202a;可能確實是如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4635290000t" end="4653600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle105">&#x202a;我現在發現了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4662650000t" end="4688930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle106">&#x202a;我一直希望月是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4732390000t" end="4756050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle107">&#x202a;我是會以牙還牙的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4766760000t" end="4792010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle108">&#x202a;我可是很強的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4821480000t" end="4843780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle109">&#x202a;打電話過去&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;請他們住手吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4872860000t" end="4877520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle110">&#x202a;喂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4878540000t" end="4896170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle111">&#x202a;龍崎,聽我說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4897220000t" end="4934530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle112">&#x202a;MISAMISA在「EIGHTEEN」的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;讀者投票中得了第一名&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4940930000t" end="4956850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle113">&#x202a;是這樣嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4957950000t" end="4997310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle114">&#x202a;也就是說她成了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;西中導演下部片的女主角了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5009670000t" end="5020930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle115">&#x202a;怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5022010000t" end="5048630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle116">&#x202a;松田那個傻蛋又在耍白癡了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5049710000t" end="5074620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle117">&#x202a;沒辦法,他天生就是這樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5082070000t" end="5097650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle118">&#x202a;我可是聽得到的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5122110000t" end="5152030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle119">&#x202a;(兩個月後)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5189180000t" end="5227860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle120">&#x202a;龍崎,我知道你沒幹勁&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不過還是請你過來一下&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5236230000t" end="5269220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle121">&#x202a;仔細看一下,不太正常吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5283940000t" end="5332630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle122">&#x202a;3個人都是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;日本著名企業中的重要員工&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5339660000t" end="5362980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle123">&#x202a;這3個人都死於心臟麻痺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5370690000t" end="5412670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle124">&#x202a;結果讓四葉的股價上漲&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;其他企業則下跌&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5419080000t" end="5452410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle125">&#x202a;也就是說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;對四葉而言這3個人死的正好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5460120000t" end="5500050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle126">&#x202a;我一調查&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;發現在這3個月內竟然有13起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5507830000t" end="5519090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle127">&#x202a;你認為呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5520180000t" end="5556130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle128">&#x202a;在我看來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只能認為KIRA是在幫助四葉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5563550000t" end="5590170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle129">&#x202a;是啊,不過如果是這樣的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5591250000t" end="5627880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle130">&#x202a;這個KIRA的真正目的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就不是制裁壞人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5628950000t" end="5664560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle131">&#x202a;是啊&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可能是以制裁壞人為掩飾&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5665660000t" end="5702970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle132">&#x202a;實際是為了公司的利益而殺人的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5722710000t" end="5751720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle133">&#x202a;怎麼樣?有點幹勁了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5752740000t" end="5774350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle134">&#x202a;(死神不會依附在)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(借走死亡筆記本的人身上)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5775430000t" end="5804100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle135">&#x202a;(死神會一直依附著持有人)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(而借的人也不能進行眼球交易)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5805130000t" end="5829130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle136">&#x202a;(持有人在借出死亡筆記本時)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(死亡的話)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5830150000t" end="5851080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle137">&#x202a;(所有權就會轉移到)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(當時持有筆記本的人身上)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5856180000t" end="5909540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle138">&#x202a;不過,能夠順利進行不受懷疑&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;真有意思呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5915570000t" end="5954250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle139">&#x202a;四葉的利益和股價&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都在悄悄的上漲&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5955280000t" end="5997260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle140">&#x202a;是啊,一切都在我們的計劃之中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6007000000t" end="6046360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle141">&#x202a;不過有一件事讓我無法釋懷&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6047370000t" end="6095720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle142">&#x202a;上星期決定要殺的3個人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;怎麼都是死於心臟麻痺呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6096750000t" end="6116090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle143">&#x202a;其中一個應該要死於意外的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6125450000t" end="6142740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle144">&#x202a;關於這點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6143800000t" end="6176450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle145">&#x202a;大概是地點&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;被指定在海線公路的緣故吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6177500000t" end="6202180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle146">&#x202a;在指定的死亡時間內&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他剛好不在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6203190000t" end="6228100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle147">&#x202a;而是跟一個女的偷偷去了義大利&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6229220000t" end="6269830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle148">&#x202a;也就是說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;如果指定的死亡方式無法實現&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6270930000t" end="6306540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle149">&#x202a;KIRA就會讓他死於心臟麻痺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6311630000t" end="6331310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle150">&#x202a;所以我上次就說過了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6332320000t" end="6354960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle151">&#x202a;讓他們意外死亡或是病死就好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6356010000t" end="6391960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle152">&#x202a;就能在最短的時間內&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;讓他們死得最自然了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6400390000t" end="6414040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle153">&#x202a;不過…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6415070000t" end="6456710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle154">&#x202a;警方現在光要調查死者的死因&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就已經分身乏術了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6457780000t" end="6499760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle155">&#x202a;一般人要是能從他們3人的死&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;追查到我們的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6500820000t" end="6515490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle156">&#x202a;那個人就是神了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6525510000t" end="6546440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle157">&#x202a;而且我已經採取防範措施了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6577900000t" end="6613170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle158">&#x202a;局長,還有模木,辛苦了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6614270000t" end="6625870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle159">&#x202a;月好厲害&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6626950000t" end="6690320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle160">&#x202a;因為他的努力,發現四葉集團&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;很可能和KIRA有牽連&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6691350000t" end="6701020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle161">&#x202a;四葉?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6711370000t" end="6720010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle162">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6728050000t" end="6746360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle163">&#x202a;應該沒錯了,松田&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6762750000t" end="6812350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle164">&#x202a;我剛聽次長說,KIRA賄賂了政客&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6831150000t" end="6905210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle165">&#x202a;KIRA說只要警方不追捕KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就不會對政客下手&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6927580000t" end="6952490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle166">&#x202a;警方向KIRA屈服了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6975630000t" end="7000540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle167">&#x202a;模木已經表示決心了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7012330000t" end="7051690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle168">&#x202a;相澤,松田,如果你們有決心的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7052710000t" end="7099350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle169">&#x202a;就馬上和我還有模木&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;一起到警署去遞辭呈吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7113430000t" end="7154040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle170">&#x202a;不辭職的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就沒辦法再認真追捕KIRA了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7155140000t" end="7173110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle171">&#x202a;什麼意思?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7180170000t" end="7194840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle172">&#x202a;很簡單&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7195850000t" end="7239190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle173">&#x202a;剛才次長說了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;和L一起追捕KIRA就會被開除&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7240230000t" end="7260480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle174">&#x202a;那麼局長呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7270260000t" end="7302570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle175">&#x202a;幾個小時後我就不是局長了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7303620000t" end="7358230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle176">&#x202a;不過大家有自己的生活&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;請考慮清楚再決定&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7359350000t" end="7400650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle177">&#x202a;是啊,特別是有家室的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7422080000t" end="7456090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle178">&#x202a;我認為大家應該回到警察崗位上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7465450000t" end="7490130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle179">&#x202a;我本來就是獨自行動的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7491150000t" end="7525160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle180">&#x202a;我感謝各位一直留到現在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7532850000t" end="7557760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle181">&#x202a;不過我一個人也可以&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7569220000t" end="7622920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle182">&#x202a;而且我一定會把KIRA的人頭&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;作為禮物送給警方&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7629280000t" end="7670240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle183">&#x202a;龍崎&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只要有我在,你就不是一個人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7671330000t" end="7684980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle184">&#x202a;而且我們還有這個約定&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7693350000t" end="7709620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle185">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7710700000t" end="7756320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle186">&#x202a;在抓到KIRA之前&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;請月和我一起行動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7757410000t" end="7795750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle187">&#x202a;不過其他各位&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還是回到警察崗位上比較好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7796780000t" end="7842060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle188">&#x202a;你不是說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;要破這個案子需要警方協助嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7843160000t" end="7894810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle189">&#x202a;那也得要警方是站在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不與KIRA妥協的基礎上才行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7895880000t" end="7935470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle190">&#x202a;辭去警察工作的幾個平民來協助&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7936590000t" end="7959570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle191">&#x202a;根本稱不上是警方的協助&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7973960000t" end="8020950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle192">&#x202a;現在警方決定不再追捕KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那就算了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8034690000t" end="8098060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle193">&#x202a;失去警察身份的我們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;確實可能幫不上什麼大忙&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8099090000t" end="8129350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle194">&#x202a;但是你要如何撫平我們的心情?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8130450000t" end="8153770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle195">&#x202a;我們可是一直努力到今天&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8154810000t" end="8209760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle196">&#x202a;我們應該有權決定要留下來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還是回警察崗位的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8210860000t" end="8253860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle197">&#x202a;說的也是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那麼請做決定吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8254910000t" end="8274590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle198">&#x202a;可…可是,局長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8275600000t" end="8309960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle199">&#x202a;要是辭去警察工作的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就失業了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8310960000t" end="8351570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle200">&#x202a;即使抓住了KIRA,那之後怎麼辦?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8361680000t" end="8392960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle201">&#x202a;之後嗎?我沒有考慮過&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8394050000t" end="8420670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle202">&#x202a;但是抓住KIRA之後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8439760000t" end="8455680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle203">&#x202a;應該可以復職吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8470790000t" end="8509810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle204">&#x202a;決定了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我也要辭去警察工作追捕KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8510830000t" end="8537790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle205">&#x202a;反正我是MISAMISA的經紀人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8538860000t" end="8566500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle206">&#x202a;而且要是現在回警署的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就像認輸了一樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8567550000t" end="8591210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle207">&#x202a;松田,注意你的用詞&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8685670000t" end="8720940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle208">&#x202a;回警察崗位&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;抽空協助辦案可以嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8727380000t" end="8740000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle209">&#x202a;不行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8741060000t" end="8772340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle210">&#x202a;要是回警察崗位的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就請不要再來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8784100000t" end="8798770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle211">&#x202a;我絕不會洩漏情報的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8799790000t" end="8825730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle212">&#x202a;我絕對不會告訴你的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8847830000t" end="8877750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle213">&#x202a;你要以警察身份追捕KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是你的自由&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8886210000t" end="8942870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle214">&#x202a;但是,如果為了追捕KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;失去警察工作還給家人添麻煩…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8943930000t" end="8963610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle215">&#x202a;我就不認為這是正確的決定&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8972290000t" end="9013930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle216">&#x202a;龍崎說的對&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你退出也不會有人怪你的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9015000000t" end="9051290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle217">&#x202a;是啊,沒人會認為你是叛徒的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9052370000t" end="9075010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle218">&#x202a;但是局長也是有家人的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9085070000t" end="9109410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle219">&#x202a;我和你的立場不同&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9128780000t" end="9164390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle220">&#x202a;真狡猾&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我也想在這裡做下去的啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9172490000t" end="9207410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle221">&#x202a;其實我早就做好&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;隨時犧牲的準備了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9219540000t" end="9252870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle222">&#x202a;要是退出的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我怎麼對得起宇生田呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9259580000t" end="9298940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle223">&#x202a;可惡,為什麼身為警察&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就不能追捕KIRA了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9315300000t" end="9325540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle224">&#x202a;龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9338660000t" end="9375970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle225">&#x202a;不管搜查總部的人發生什麼情況&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9377030000t" end="9406950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle226">&#x202a;就算是被警方開除&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9408060000t" end="9454360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle227">&#x202a;也要給他們及其家人經濟資助&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9455440000t" end="9481720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle228">&#x202a;你不是一開始就指示過了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9482800000t" end="9511810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle229">&#x202a;為什麼不告訴他們?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9521840000t" end="9546750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle230">&#x202a;渡,別多嘴&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9547870000t" end="9562200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle231">&#x202a;對不起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9563220000t" end="9603150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle232">&#x202a;什麼嘛&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;原來你連這個問題都考慮過了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9604260000t" end="9626900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle233">&#x202a;相澤,這樣不是很好嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9684670000t" end="9738710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle234">&#x202a;龍崎,你在試探我&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;肯不肯辭職跟你一起調查嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9739730000t" end="9760660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle235">&#x202a;不是這樣的,相澤&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9761750000t" end="9794060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle236">&#x202a;龍崎只是不喜歡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;自己親口說出來而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9795110000t" end="9811380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle237">&#x202a;是啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9812460000t" end="9820760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle238">&#x202a;不&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9841160000t" end="9879840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle239">&#x202a;我是在試探你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;看你會怎麼選擇&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9888540000t" end="9899460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle240">&#x202a;龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9945600000t" end="9959590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle241">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9960610000t" end="9980520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle242">&#x202a;我不幹了,我要回警局&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9981630000t" end="9998240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle243">&#x202a;相澤&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9999320000t" end="10038340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle244">&#x202a;我沒有局長你們這樣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;立即下決心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10039360000t" end="10065980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle245">&#x202a;老是想著要回警署去&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10067050000t" end="10084000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle246">&#x202a;別這麼固執了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10085070000t" end="10103380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle247">&#x202a;不,我不幹了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10104420000t" end="10121370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle248">&#x202a;現在我又更加確認了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10129110000t" end="10167450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle249">&#x202a;我討厭龍崎,討厭他的所有做法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10190510000t" end="10224520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle250">&#x202a;不過我很喜歡相澤先生這樣的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10261910000t" end="10307530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle251">&#x202a;這種時候還睜眼說瞎話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我也很討厭你這一點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10308630000t" end="10322280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle252">&#x202a;我要退出了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10330650000t" end="10343620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle253">&#x202a;辛苦你了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10471460000t" end="10488410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle254">&#x202a;又有發現了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10489470000t" end="10571500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle255">&#x202a;四葉最大競爭對手的分行長官&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在9月7日從家中樓梯跌落死亡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10572560000t" end="10597810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle256">&#x202a;9月7日,那是星期五吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10605590000t" end="10634260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle257">&#x202a;我重新調查過一遍,結果發現…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10635290000t" end="10678290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle258">&#x202a;對四葉有利的死亡案件&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都集中在週末&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10679330000t" end="10690590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle259">&#x202a;真的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10698020000t" end="10731350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle260">&#x202a;一開始死亡的日期很分散&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10732380000t" end="10775380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle261">&#x202a;之後漸漸集中在星期五晚上&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;到星期六下午之間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10776430000t" end="10799750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle262">&#x202a;局長,真是了不起的發現&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10800790000t" end="10826040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle263">&#x202a;我說過我已經不是局長了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10827140000t" end="10857740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle264">&#x202a;不,對我來說你永遠是局長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10858840000t" end="10884440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle265">&#x202a;爸爸,這一定是重要的線索&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10885540000t" end="10925470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle266">&#x202a;我也不能輸給你和龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10926580000t" end="10950240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle267">&#x202a;我可不想成為這裡的包袱&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10956610000t" end="10973220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle268">&#x202a;包袱&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10974290000t" end="10995900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle269">&#x202a;KIRA是在四葉集團之中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10996980000t" end="11020980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle270">&#x202a;或是在利用四葉集團&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11022010000t" end="11037590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle271">&#x202a;目前還不清楚&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11038690000t" end="11067360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle272">&#x202a;但確定可以從KIRA這方面來調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11074390000t" end="11095320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle273">&#x202a;要徹底調查四葉集團&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11111430000t" end="11149430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle274">&#x202a;這是四葉集團國內外員工的名單&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我整理出來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11150470000t" end="11160140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle275">&#x202a;謝謝&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11166150000t" end="11206420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle276">&#x202a;超過30萬人耶&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這麼快就整理出來啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11207520000t" end="11225490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle277">&#x202a;模木先生好厲害&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11226540000t" end="11256460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle278">&#x202a;模木一直是話不多卻埋頭苦幹的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11257570000t" end="11271560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle279">&#x202a;龍…龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11272590000t" end="11311270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle280">&#x202a;除了經紀人工作之外&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有什麼我可以幫得上忙的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11319970000t" end="11340900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle281">&#x202a;你想幫上忙嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11341990000t" end="11352910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle282">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11354000000t" end="11375610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle283">&#x202a;那請再幫我倒杯咖啡來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11391710000t" end="11414350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle284">&#x202a;也幫那邊的客人倒一杯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11439760000t" end="11465360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle285">&#x202a;是誰?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;什麼時候進來的?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11478130000t" end="11505430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle286">&#x202a;他們是我們的新成員&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11539520000t" end="11573530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle287">&#x202a;我是亞柏&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是個騙子,請多指教&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11574560000t" end="11605160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle288">&#x202a;我叫溫蒂,職業是小偷&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11606260000t" end="11634240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle289">&#x202a;騙子跟小偷?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11635290000t" end="11644610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle290">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11650970000t" end="11720030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle291">&#x202a;亞柏是具備一切社交技巧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可以和目標建立親密關係的騙子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11721040000t" end="11737650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle292">&#x202a;方便進行臥底的工作&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11744390000t" end="11793990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle293">&#x202a;溫蒂是可以破解任何鎖&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;和入侵安全系統的小偷&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11795110000t" end="11841410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle294">&#x202a;她在我們沒發覺的情況下進來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就是最好的證明&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11842490000t" end="11868090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle295">&#x202a;要我們和罪犯一起工作嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11869190000t" end="11883520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle296">&#x202a;雖然是罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11884530000t" end="11925830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle297">&#x202a;但和那些被KIRA制裁的貨色不同&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11926910000t" end="11955580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle298">&#x202a;就把他們當做是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;見不得光的專家吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11956610000t" end="11969230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle299">&#x202a;原來如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11970290000t" end="12003280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle300">&#x202a;想要調查四葉集團&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;的確需要這樣的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12016000000t" end="12037950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle301">&#x202a;大家同心協力加油吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12039020000t" end="12045610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle302">&#x202a;嗯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12046700000t" end="12061030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle303">&#x202a;好…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12208190000t" end="12217170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle304">&#x202a;是爸爸耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12226880000t" end="12238140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle305">&#x202a;爸爸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12251900000t" end="12271580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle306">&#x202a;由美,惠利子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12278590000t" end="12301910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle307">&#x202a;你在這裡做什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12309630000t" end="12331580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle308">&#x202a;要回家吃飯的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;記得跟我說一聲&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12332650000t" end="12360290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle309">&#x202a;因為晚飯沒有買你的份&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12361340000t" end="12388640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle310">&#x202a;我的可樂餅分給爸爸一半好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12389710000t" end="12432370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle311">&#x202a;抱歉,好久沒休息了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以突然休假了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12443760000t" end="12463670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle312">&#x202a;休假,是指可以放假嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12464780000t" end="12479680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle313">&#x202a;沒錯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12480800000t" end="12492740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle314">&#x202a;太好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12500150000t" end="12527110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle315">&#x202a;以後每星期都有休假的時候囉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12536190000t" end="12559850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle316">&#x202a;所以不管是來公園&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12572220000t" end="12598500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle317">&#x202a;不,就算是去動物園&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12610260000t" end="12624930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle318">&#x202a;或是兒童樂園…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12663650000t" end="12674570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle319">&#x202a;你怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12699010000t" end="12732340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle320">&#x202a;媽媽,爸爸在哭&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12805120000t" end="12855400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle321">&#x202a;看見誰都無法看見的夢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12856510000t" end="12910210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle322">&#x202a;捨棄所有不需要的事物&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12911230000t" end="12943200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle323">&#x202a;無法割捨的感情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12944260000t" end="12998640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle324">&#x202a;深藏在我的心裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12999650000t" end="13063360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle325">&#x202a;依然處在現實與理想的夾縫中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13064380000t" end="13115350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle326">&#x202a;即使犧牲的伽鎖拴住敢的腳&#x202c;</p>
